text:
Aitziber Porras Conde (born 9 May 1978 Vitoria) is a Spanish rugby player. She is a member of the Spanish Women's Rugby team with 39 international caps. She played for Gaztedi Rugby Taldea.
She participated at the 2003 Women's Six Nations Championship, 2004 Women's Six Nations Championship, 2005 Women's Six Nations Championship, 2006 Women's Six Nations Championship, 2002 Women's Rugby World Cup, and 2006 Women's Rugby World Cup.
She participated at the 2009 FIRA Women's European Trophy.
